The United States strongly condemns the hostage situation and violence that occurred in Baghdad, Iraq, on Sunday, which was carried out by terrorists linked to al Qaeda. Many innocent Iraqis were killed in this senseless act. The US expresses its condolences to the families of the victims and the people of Iraq, who have been targeted by these acts of terrorism. The US stands with the majority of Iraqis who reject violence and is committed to working together to combat terrorism and protect both nations' people.